flowchart TD
  %% CallScore canonical agentic platform map. No secrets. Netlify + HH PostgreSQL/HH Read API are canonical.

  subgraph PublicProduct[Public Product]
    Visitor[Public visitor / buyer]
    Netlify[Netlify CallScore app\ncall-score.com]
    PublicAPI[Next.js public/API routes]
    Visitor --> Netlify --> PublicAPI
  end

  subgraph CanonicalDataPlane[Canonical Data Plane]
    HHRead[HH Read API\npublic read source]
    PG[(Local HH PostgreSQL\ncanonical production DB)]
    PublicAPI --> HHRead --> PG
  end

  subgraph TranscriptCollection[Transcript Collection]
    YT[YouTube / creator source data]
    Laptop[Omar laptop\nTailscale + residential browser cookies\nlaptop-side yt-dlp]
    Ingest[Approved transcript ingest path\nbounded writes only]
    HHFallback[HH yt-dlp / ASR / vpn-ytdlp\ndiagnostic future fallback only]
    YT --> Laptop --> Ingest --> PG
    YT -. diagnostic only .-> HHFallback -. terminal evidence / future canary .-> Ingest
  end

  subgraph IntelligencePipeline[Scoring / Intelligence Pipeline]
    Extract[Claim extraction\nrule path + shadow model canaries]
    Ollama[Local Ollama\nGemma / Qwen shadow + diff]
    Match[Matching / symbol normalization]
    Score[Scoring / freshness / audit]
    PublicRows[Public-safe ranked rows\nmonetization target fields gated]
    PG --> Extract
    Extract --> Ollama --> Extract
    Extract --> Match --> Score --> PublicRows --> HHRead
  end

  subgraph AgenticControl[Agentic Control Plane]
    Hermes[Hermes control plane\n/srv/agents/hermes]
    Workplane[Workplane readiness + job registry\nCONTROLLED_FULL]
    HHBridge[HH control bridge\n/srv/agents/hh-control-bridge]
    Receipts[Workflow receipts\n.tmp/workflow-receipts]
    Docs[Docs / handovers / memory\nREADME + architecture + agentmemory]
    Library[Local library catalog\n/srv/agents/library]
    Hermes --> Workplane --> HHBridge
    Workplane --> Receipts
    Workplane --> Docs
    Hermes --> Library
    Workplane -. monitors .-> PG
    Workplane -. monitors .-> Netlify
  end

  subgraph CommercialPlane[Commercial / Entitlement Plane]
    WhopAuto[Whop Auto\n/srv/whop-auto]
    Whop[Whop checkout / entitlement\nzero-dollar token proof recorded]
    Entitlement[Pro / Alpha entitlement checks]
    WhopAuto --> Whop --> Entitlement --> PublicAPI
  end

  subgraph GrowthPlane[Marketing / Growth Plane]
    Art[Art of War automation\n/srv/agents/repos/Claude_Code_Automations]
    Packet[Private campaign dry-run\napproval_packet_ready]
    OwnedCanary[Owned-channel publish canary\nrequires approval receipt]
    Art --> Packet --> OwnedCanary
  end

  subgraph ConnectedApps[Composio Connected Apps]
    Composio[Composio MCP hub\nread-only inventory ready]
    Attio[Attio CRM]
    Gmail[Gmail / email]
    X[Twitter / X]
    PostHog[PostHog]
    HF[Hugging Face\nComposio auth initiated; HF plugin separate]
    LinkedIn[LinkedIn]
    Discord[Discord]
    Composio --> Attio
    Composio --> Gmail
    Composio --> X
    Composio --> PostHog
    Composio --> HF
    Composio --> LinkedIn
    Composio --> Discord
    Art -. read-only / gated actions .-> Composio
    Workplane -. inventory .-> Composio
  end

  subgraph SafetyGates[Safety Gates / Receipts]
    Monitored[Monitored gates\ntranscript backlog\nHTTP 429 cooldown\nGemma manual-review deltas\nComposio non-core gaps]
    FailClosed[Fail-closed gates\npaid spend\npublic sends/posts without approval\nWhop pricing/product/customer/payment mutation\ndestructive SQL/infra\nbroad DB backfills\ncredential rotation\nsecret exposure\n429 hammer retry]
    Rollback[Rollback path\nrestore PARTIAL/BLOCKED if core checks fail]
    Receipts --> Monitored
    Receipts --> FailClosed
    Monitored --> Rollback
    FailClosed --> Rollback
  end

  Workplane -. controls .-> TranscriptCollection
  Workplane -. controls .-> IntelligencePipeline
  Workplane -. controls .-> CommercialPlane
  Workplane -. controls .-> GrowthPlane
  Workplane -. records .-> SafetyGates
